{"lang": "zh_CN", "eventid": "act51side", "eventName": "人们，我们", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "PA-1", "avgTag": "行动前", "storyName": "“卡托加区欢迎你”", "storyInfo": "在一年一度的冬季舞会上，娜塔莉娅见识到了形形色色的贵族，并独自收集情报。在这些贵族为政治吵得不可开交时，前来抗议的学生们包围了舞会厅。", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "72_g7_ballroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.1, "fillto": 0.1, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.1, "fillto": 0.1, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheeledshoe_carpet_fts", "volume": 0.0, "channel": "f", "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.8, "channel": "f", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一路走来，走廊上都只点着蜡烛。连皇宫也减少了电的用度吗？这真是......", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "为将储存的能源节省起来分给民众，陛下是这样说的。", "name": "殷勤的近侍"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不过请您放心，这只是陛下出于勤俭节约的提议，宫中的生活并没有受到影响，今年的冬季舞会也是如此。", "name": "殷勤的近侍"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们就要到了。罗斯托娃小姐，请让我为您取下大衣。", "name": "殷勤的近侍"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "f", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothtrailground"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.8}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheeledshoe_carpet_fts", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感谢您的帮助。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "职责所在。", "name": "殷勤的近侍"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$ouat_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "72_g7_ballroom", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.2, "duration": 4.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#4$1", "duration": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好亮......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#4$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1982_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那么，我就退下了。祝您愉快。", "name": "殷勤的近侍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1982_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "60,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.1}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#3$1", "posfrom": "-35,0", "posto": "35,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.1}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烦请稍等，我还有一些问题——", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#3$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——娜塔申卡？", "name": "贵族女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？您是......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#6$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沃伦佐娃伯爵夫人？", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#6$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-80,0", "posto": "110,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下在上......可怜的孩子，真的是你。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "稍远处的贵妇人看见了早露，立即快步迎了上来，惊喜的神情几乎让她有失贵族仪态。"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她紧紧握住了早露的小臂，像是在努力确认眼前的女孩并不是幻影。"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "posfrom": "110,0", "posto": "20,0", "duration": 1.8}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.8}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜塔申卡......实在是太好了，我还能见到你......健康活着的你。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我听说了发生在切尔诺伯格的事情，我的心简直都要碎了。我实在是不明白，命运为何要让如此善良的一家人遭受这样可怕的事......", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "承蒙您的挂念，虽说损失了些产业，但比起全家人的安危来说，那些已经不值一提了......总之，都过去了。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#8$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，是的，快让我们忘了那些不好的回忆吧......你不知道，我在收到你的信，得知你要来圣骏堡的时候有多高兴。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真希望你能够在这过上一段平静的日子，可如你所见，现在的圣骏堡也不是一个安稳平静的地方。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到处都是心怀不满的人，到处都是不知感恩的抱怨——仿佛那些无礼的军人闹得还不够似的，吵闹的平民也恨不得将圣骏堡翻个底朝天。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#13$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，瞧我。你刚回来，恐怕还不知道。为近来这些事，我终日精神紧绷，多梦少眠，可见到老友的孩子，总归不该一上来就说这些。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不会的，只要是您说的，我都愿意听。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#11$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是个好孩子，但现在却不是提这些事的好时候。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告诉我，娜塔申卡。你母亲身体还好吗？你父亲安德烈如今又在何处？", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果他来了圣骏堡，却没遣人告知于我，只让你来参加冬季舞会......", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想来，应该是因为我们两家已经生分太久，我实在不算是个合格的朋友。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是这样的，沃伦佐娃夫人。父亲曾说，如果能在这里见到您，就让我代他向您致意，请您宽恕他的久疏问候。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#8$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至于母亲那边就更不必说了，您当然是她最要好的女友，可罗斯托夫家族如今必须想办法将中部仅剩的那些产业紧紧抓住。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#8$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我们切不可再丢失任何体面。”所以，非常遗憾......他们在短时间内都脱不开身。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#5$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我了解了。但是孩子，你最后应该说的是：“所以，我就在这里了。”", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看你，已经是一个成熟体面的姑娘了，可以代表罗斯托夫家族了，不是吗？", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我得说，你的仪态与教养，比许多生斯长斯的圣骏堡人都更为优秀——我相信用不了多久，圣骏堡会记住罗斯托夫这个姓氏的。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不......我很清楚自己还有许多要学的事务。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "说起这点，夫人，其实我很想向您请教，关于圣骏堡现在的局势......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年轻的娜塔申卡，不要着急，我了解你的困惑，但这不是三言两语就能说清楚的问题。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要学会用自己的眼睛去看，不会有比现在更好的机会了，你现在最应该做的就是——先好好享受这场冬季舞会。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在陛下到来之前，抛开那些恼人的问题、急于知道的答案，以及所有有关未来将会如何的奇谈怪论，只是享受当下。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去舞蹈，去嬉笑，去做年轻人应当做的事。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你看上某位青年军官，就算是那个老顽固博尔孔斯基家的，为了你母亲，我也会豁出这张老脸去替你说媒——", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "总之，在陛下的庇护下安宁地享乐，这是属于首都，属于我们这些忠诚的人的特权。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜塔申卡，你必须先学会这点，才能真正融入其中。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.1, "fillto": 0.01, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.1, "fillto": 0.01, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "72_g2_sjbstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“......你必须先学会这点，才能真正融入其中。”", "multi": "true", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2156_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......矿工们仍在挨饿，哪怕是在圣骏堡，奥多耶夫区的居民也都已经用不起暖气，卡托加区更是在停工之后，被彻底切断了供电和供暖。", "name": "真理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2156_1#2$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2156_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算这样，他们也还是要享乐。", "name": "真理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2156_1#2$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_196_sunbr_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不明白......那个人不是说，陛下节省了皇宫的用电吗？那些省下来的能源呢？为什么——", "name": "古米"}, "figure_art": "avg_196_sunbr_1#5$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这都聊的些什么乌七八糟的，“大人物”就是麻烦。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_196_sunbr_1#21$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，早露姐一个人在里面，真的没关系吗？", "name": "古米"}, "figure_art": "avg_196_sunbr_1#21$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2156_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "学生联合大会召开的前几天，娜塔莉娅就和我们商量了，她会以罗斯托夫家继承人的身份进入舞会，探查情报。", "name": "真理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2156_1#11$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2156_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "毕竟，总有些东西是只有贵族才知道，其他人都被蒙在鼓里的。无论是哪方面的情报，多掌握些总不会错。", "name": "真理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2156_1#8$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2156_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "索尼娅相信她能做好，我也没有反对的理由。除了这些我们早就有所预料的对话内容，目前听起来还算顺利，监听设备的声音也算清晰。", "name": "真理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2156_1#8$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "avgdisplay", "attributes": {"id": "1", "style": "bg", "name": "bg_black", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.6, "duration": 2.0, "slot": "bgover", "layer": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"maskid": "ui_cutin_mask_horizon", "char": "伯塔尼", "size": "1300,380", "style": 2.0, "offset": "0,20", "channel": 3.0, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 1.0, "slot": "m", "sfrom": "1.25,1.25", "sto": "1,1", "sduration": 0.3, "pfrom": "80,20", "pto": "0,20", "name": "cutin_char_23", "duration": 6.0, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 2.0, "name": "72_g3_podium", "sfrom": "1.25,1.25", "sto": "1.1,1.1", "sduration": 0.3, "pfrom": "100,20", "pto": "0,20", "duration": 5.0, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "得亏那位叫“伯塔尼”的学生，她的设备比想象中可靠。", "name": "烈夏"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "clear": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "avgdisplay", "attributes": {"id": "1", "style": "bg", "name": "bg_black", "afrom": 0.6, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.7, "slot": "bgover", "layer": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "avgdisplay", "attributes": {"id": "1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2156_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下来，我们只需要按计划配合示威行动就行。", "name": "真理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2156_1#8$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_196_sunbr_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凛冬姐好像在那边招手，我们该过去会合了！", "name": "古米"}, "figure_art": "avg_196_sunbr_1#9$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2156_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "应该是她已经和其他人沟通好了。我们收拾一下，这就过去。", "name": "真理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2156_1#8$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2156_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烈夏，你是留在这里还是？", "name": "真理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2156_1#4$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，等下，先别说话。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#7$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像有情况......", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#7$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "72_g7_ballroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$ouat_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我还以为，今年的冬季舞会不会举办了......", "name": "担忧的贵族"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那群无礼的叛臣，竟敢矜仗武力威逼我们的皇帝陛下。可我也实在不知道，我们的陛下到底该拿他们怎样为好......", "name": "担忧的贵族"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "越是这种时刻，我们越要挺起胸膛，继续必要的活动。陛下有这样的勇气，也有这样的远见。", "name": "骄傲的贵族"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因为这是比什么举动都有力的反击，证明这动乱不足为惧，我们不会被已经失败过一次的叛徒击溃。", "name": "骄傲的贵族"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至于那些看不清现状，选择支持叛乱者的家伙......我们只需要来年去他们的墓前，献上一束百合花。", "name": "骄傲的贵族"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#4$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小心！", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#7$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_splashwine"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#7$1", "posfrom": "170,0", "posto": "145,0", "duration": 0.2}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#4$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "posfrom": "210,0", "posto": "30,0", "duration": 0.6, "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.1}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#4$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "posfrom": "30,0", "posto": "10,0", "duration": 0.5, "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——抱歉——", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#4$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......先不论这位好心小姐的裙子，您的莽撞可是弄洒了一杯好酒，这位......不知名的先生。", "name": "骄傲的贵族"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，真的非常抱歉！请原谅我的无礼，沃尔金娜公爵阁下——", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#10$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您没有冒犯到我，您现在更应当对这位被弄脏了裙子的小姐道歉。", "name": "骄傲的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#10$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，那这位......", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#4$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没关系。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是谁把这么冒失的家伙放进来了？", "name": "担忧的贵族"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他能被侍者放进来，总不会是什么籍籍无名的小市民。您的名字是？", "name": "骄傲的贵族"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦！您可以叫我巴普洛维奇，下议院的一名小小议员，最近刚被陛下授予了枢密官官秩，是卡托加区近期事务的特别全权代表——", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡托加区的代表？啊，我想起来了。", "name": "骄傲的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您竟然记得我，这可真是无上的荣幸！", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#6$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "当然，当然。我听说议会迟迟没有找到人选来处理卡托加区这个大麻烦，这份重任最后落在了您的头上，想必您一定有过人之处吧。", "name": "骄傲的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#6$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不是我近来忙于为第二集团军调度冬季物资，一定会亲自派人上门祝贺。", "name": "骄傲的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#6$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公爵阁下实在是谬赞了......其实，我已经在卡托加区上任两个月了。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#2$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不知道自己究竟是何德何能，会被委以重任，但的确不敢让陛下失望。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#2$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您应该知道的，卡托加区并不如大家所说的那样一文不值，这个老工业区只是缺一个重新焕发生机的机会......", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#2$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小声）我怎么没听说有这样一号人物？", "name": "担忧的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#2$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在自己那奢华的庄园里休养了太久，不了解中枢人员变动也是常事。坐在花园摇椅里百无聊赖的时候，至少多看看报纸吧。", "name": "骄傲的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#2$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，看了也只是徒增烦扰。", "name": "担忧的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#2$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不不......我实在不值得格利岑伯爵阁下劳神关注——我听说伯爵阁下的酒庄今年生意非常兴盛，想必您应该十分繁忙......", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先不要急着献殷勤——您是不是还欠这位小姐一个正式的道歉？", "name": "骄傲的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这位热心的小姐，您怎么称呼？", "name": "骄傲的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尊敬的公爵阁下，我叫娜塔莉娅·罗斯托娃。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#8$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "罗斯托娃？这个姓氏倒是没怎么听说过......", "name": "骄傲的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#8$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也没有。", "name": "担忧的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#8$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦！您的父亲一定就是切尔诺伯格的安德烈伯爵吧。", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没想到您竟然会知道家父......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#6$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "当然，您的父亲是个有远见的人，他及时从切城抽身而出，才不至于让全副身家都丢在那里——的确十分有智慧！", "name": "巴普洛维奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2158_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......都已经是过去的事了。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#13$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没想到，巴普洛维奇先生，还真是......博闻强识。", "name": "骄傲的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#13$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不过，还是先去换掉你的裙子吧，孩子。即使是再醇厚的美酒，也不是为了让绸缎品尝而酿造的。", "name": "骄傲的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#13$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的，谢谢您......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#3$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheeledshoe_carpet_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "60,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.8, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早露匆匆离开了这个令自己窘迫的场合，隐约还能听到身后人们热切的谈论。"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沃尔金娜公爵阁下！我听说，您不支持将卡托加区全面停用的提议，当然，我也一样......", "name": "殷勤的声音"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......这其中的产业，依然......", "name": "殷勤的声音"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......也许我们能合作......", "name": "殷勤的声音"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "72_g7_ballroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......请注意你的措辞，梅利尼科夫先生。目前连陛下都还没有对远北事宜下定论。", "name": "严肃的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大人，您误会了我的意思，我刚才的话绝非是在对您或者女大公个人进行指责。", "name": "傲慢的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，我早在叶莉萨维塔把远北搅得乌烟瘴气前，就已多次表达过对布列洁诺伊的担忧，而你们当时却齐声向陛下保证她的忠诚。", "name": "傲慢的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以是你们，你们老一派的每个人，都辜负了议会与陛下的信任。", "name": "傲慢的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就期盼你在听证会上也能如此慷慨陈词，最好一字不改，让所有人知道，你如何妄言乌萨斯的基石们。", "name": "严肃的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必等到那个时候，大人。", "name": "傲慢的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今晚皇帝陛下莅临会场，我一定会向他本人痛诉你们的罪行！", "name": "傲慢的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怒叱声惹来了在场许多人的目光，几位侍从赶忙上前，试图平息大人物不知因何而起的怒火。"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#4$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早露拢了拢衣袖，稍稍驱散寒意，尽管舞会厅的壁炉比乌萨斯任何一处都烧得更热，暖气也终日供应着。"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一旁的侍从正在更换香薰，浓郁的佛手柑与橙花的气味，遮掩住酒精挥发的辛辣，早露长吁一口气。"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你还好吗，娜塔申卡？还是没有找到合适的聊天人选？", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦天哪，你的裙子——是谁轻慢你了吗？把那人的名字告诉我，我一定狠狠给他一个教训！", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是的，夫人，您实在不必为此生气。这是我帮助了一位女士所留下的“勋章”呢。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#8$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是个热心的孩子，但答应我，下次先保证自己的安全，好吗？谁知道那些谄媚的家伙会做出什么事。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感谢您的关心，可这算得上是今晚头等有趣的好事了。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今晚我所听到的大都与那位女大公有关。我试着去了解，去询问，却始终因为对这类话题缺乏必要的知识，导致对话无法进行下去。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#12$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这就是你父母让你来到圣骏堡的作用了，我亲爱的娜塔申卡。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我见过许多年轻的小姐，宁可把灵魂托付给厨师、裁缝和医生，也不愿分神给那些制定法律、平定叛乱、敲定赋税的伟人......", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使是他们始终在照看着我们。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您说的道理，我都明白，可我如今只是一个中部小伯爵的继承人，又怎么会得到这些人在百忙之中才会抽出空来的注视呢？", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#5$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你是我老友的独生女，我必须得把话讲得更明白。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没有人能脱离政治而生存，尤其你承袭了贵族的头衔，它已经赋予了你沉重的责任。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#14$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这样的责任，是通过在这里轻松地谈论一些事物就能实现的吗......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#14$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜塔申卡......", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你误解了我们在这里高谈阔论的缘由。这些话语并不是为了宣告一定会被落实的举措，也不是为了表明我们真正的意见。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是为了......什么呢？", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#10$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "为了合群，孩子。为了迅速与一些人划清界限，又与另一些人结为同盟。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一份签名文件，或许就能让你的父母东山再起，让你的儿女远离战壕，让你的朋友都在庄园里安稳入眠。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要以为沉浸享乐就能逃离他们的目光，这只会让他们照看你的方式变得粗暴，且不容置疑。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真正高效的社交场合就是这样运作的，我的娜塔申卡。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......看来我要学习的还有很多。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所幸，年轻人最不缺的就是时间了。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodfloor_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（低声）是议长阁下——", "name": "贵族A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "还有瓦西里副议长！真稀奇，他们几乎不在议会之外的地方一同出现......", "name": "贵族B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "议长阁下很少参加舞会，但陛下还迟迟没有驾临......这，是否是某种信号？", "name": "贵族A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也许是想安抚我们。", "name": "贵族B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那恐怕来得有些晚了。", "name": "贵族A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那两位......？", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#6$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crowdtalk_fear", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在二人到来的第一时间，整个舞会的目光都聚集在了他们身上。人们自动为两人的到来分出一条道路，通向舞会厅的正中央。"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人群中发出声音响亮但不知情绪真假的问候。"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "avgdisplay", "attributes": {"id": "1", "style": "bg", "name": "bg_black", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.6, "duration": 2.0, "slot": "bgover", "layer": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2172_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 1.0, "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 1.0, "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我们敬爱的议长阁下，向您致敬。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "multi": "true", "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2169_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 1.0, "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“尊敬的副议长阁下，祝您身体健康。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "multi": "true", "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "avgdisplay", "attributes": {"id": "1", "style": "bg", "name": "bg_black", "afrom": 0.6, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "slot": "bgover", "layer": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "avgdisplay", "attributes": {"id": "1"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#10$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.5, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早露挤在人群中，小心地打量起二人。"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodfloor_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.8}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1984_1#1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑发的男人沉默地从人群中走过，脸上不见喜怒，眼神坚定却难掩疲惫，只是看向空无一物的前方。"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodfloor_fts", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.8}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#2$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被称为“副议长”的男人走在明显矮他一头的黑发男人身后，恭敬地维持着半个身位的距离，同时以温和的笑容向人们点头致意。"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......金发的那位，是瓦西里·戈尔奇科夫公爵，近卫军荣誉上将，也是帝国议会的常务副议长。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（低声）而走在他前面，黑发的那位——", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊斯拉姆·维特议长。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#1$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是了......每个立足在圣骏堡的人都不该不认识他。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，夫人，是我在城际网络上看过他演讲的视频。《在图利斯卡亚特别技术学校落成仪式上的演说》，内容简洁真挚，令人印象深刻。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#2$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，城际网络......我可能永远也弄不清这些时髦玩意。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去吧，娜塔申卡，到他们跟前去。去听听那些人都在说些什么，这也是学习的好时机。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的，夫人。那么，我这就——", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#1$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_phntsmglsbrek", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "volume": 0.0, "channel": "f", "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.8, "channel": "f", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "清脆的玻璃破碎声响，在舞会厅各处愉悦的高谈阔论中显得如此刺耳，人们不禁寻找它的源头。"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奥萨奇伯爵，您身体有什么不适吗？", "name": "贵族A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不，不不，是他们来了，他们在楼下！", "name": "贵族B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spotlightc", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paniccrowd", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什么？哪个天杀的把电闸关了——难道是停电了？", "name": "贵族A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1"}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，皇宫怎么会突然停电？肯定是暴民——", "name": "贵族B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1"}, {"id": 447, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_recorderglitch", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.8, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "f", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "皇宫的勤务官就是这么办事的吗，连个电闸都维护不好——", "name": "贵族A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1981_1#1$1"}, {"id": 460, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......快看外面！", "name": "贵族B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1"}, {"id": 462, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的有暴民，还正在我们的窗外！", "name": "贵族B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1"}, {"id": 463, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 465, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 467, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 468, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 469, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}